# The 2001 ns-2.29 DiffServ4NS sources under src/ns-2.29/ are frozen
# per CLAUDE.md ("Do not modify files under ns2/. The 2001 ns-2 module
# is read-only, period."). Accidentally reformatting them (manually or
# via an IDE / agent) would violate that rule silently. This file opts
# the entire subtree out of clang-format.
#
# The ancestor walkup stops here, not at the project-root .clang-format,
# so both manual clang-format invocations and check-style-clang-format.py
# respect the disable.
---
Language: Cpp
DisableFormat: true
SortIncludes: Never
...
